commentAnnotations.text: The respective procedure for illiterate patients (if included) is described in the Appendix 10.1.
For Japan only: The following events will be handled as 'deemed serious for any other reason': AEs which possibly lead to disability will be reported as SAEs.
Cancers of new histology and exacerbations of existing cancer must be reported as a serious event regardless of the duration between discontinuation of the drug and the occurrence of the cancer.
